While starting in 2012, we had a pretty simple objective, and that was to be a part of the global technological revolution. Therefore, instead of bothering about achievements, we strived to contribute and make an impact through serving each of our clients at our best regardless of the size of the project or its technological significance. This way we’ve learned and grown together while empowering hundreds of other business and individuals world-wide. We continued our journey to shape up the dreams of our partners and turn even their wildest imagination into a diligent reality. Throughout these years we’ve reached millions of active users and been a part of their life with the offerings and services we’ve built together and we are humbly proud of that.

Till this day, more matured and experienced ‘doodle’ works closely with growing businesses as well as enthusiastic individuals who seek to take their business and ideas to the next level through the efficient use of information technology and improved digital experience. We thrive to enable them by leveraging our experience, expertise and diverse resources to their best interest, so we can keep growing together and contribute towards making this world a bit smarter and a lot better every day.

Hence, we have a low employee turnover as most of our team members are willing to remain a part of Doodle at present and even in future.
